你能够调用以下的API:
[['ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_reports', {'name': 'ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_reports', 'description': 'This function retrieves customer satisfaction reports for consumer finance companies over a specified period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The period for which the reports are requested, e.g., last_six_months.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reports', 'description': 'A list of satisfaction reports for the specified period.'}]}], ['ConsumerFinance.get_complaints', {'name': 'ConsumerFinance.get_complaints', 'description': 'This function retrieves customer complaint data for consumer finance companies on a specific date.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date for which the complaint data is requested, in YYYY-MM-DD format.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'complaints', 'description': 'A list of customer complaints for the specified date.'}]}], ['ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_scores', {'name': 'ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_scores', 'description': 'This function retrieves current customer satisfaction scores for consumer finance companies.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'scores', 'description': 'Current satisfaction scores for the companies.'}]}], ['ConsumerFinance.get_service_strategies', {'name': 'ConsumerFinance.get_service_strategies', 'description': 'This function retrieves customer service strategies for a specific consumer finance company.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the consumer finance company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategies', 'description': 'Customer service strategies for the specified company.'}]}], ['ConsumerFinance.get_improvement_suggestions', {'name': 'ConsumerFinance.get_improvement_suggestions', 'description': 'This function retrieves suggestions for improving customer satisfaction for a specific consumer finance company.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company_name', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the consumer finance company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'suggestions', 'description': 'Suggestions for improving customer satisfaction for the specified company.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_reports` 并传入 `period`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "ConsumerFinance.get_satisfaction_reports",
    "args": "{'period': 'last_six_months'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
